      "rationale": "Testing was performed under a single standardized ASTM F1717 test condition (displacement rate 25 mm/min, ambient temperature). Only one loading rate was evaluated. This limits characterization of test condition sensitivity and results in achieved level (1) below required level (2). This is a documented gap accepted by the assessment team given the standardized nature of the ASTM protocol."
