      "rationale": "E/uval computed for construct stiffness (1.12), yield force (1.38), and force at 40 mm (1.61), all below the 1.96 threshold. Specimen-level percent differences ranged from 0.8% to 8.7%, all within the 10% acceptance bound. Achieved level (3) exceeds required level (2) due to cross-laboratory replication."
